Output sequence

i  j  lambda0  lambda1  p  rho 

Note: i and j is the number of the cell. Corresponding x- and y- coordinate should be i/cell and j/cell. cell is the parameter in ghost.hpp
      In the .vtk file, j = 1100, 1000 and 600, corresponds to the y-plane where y = 55, 50 and 30
      Temperature T = p/rho
	  